      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This unit represents a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen in truly pristine condition, boasting a flawless exterior and an interior that remains indistinguishable from new. Rigorously inspected to ensure total mechanical integrity, it offers an uncompromising driving experience for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
