    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hi there! I'm so excited to show you this absolute gem! Honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've babied this car since day one, and it's in truly flawless, pristine condition\u2014not a scratch or a smudge to be found! It drives like a dream and is ready for a new home where it'll be just as loved. You really have to see it in person to believe how beautiful it is. Feel free to reach out with any questions at all\u2014I'm happy to chat and show it to you!",
      "price": 42900.0,
