    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 1991 BMW M3 (E30) in pristine condition. This homologation special features the high-revving S14 2.3L DOHC inline-four, characterized by its individual throttle bodies and recent shim-and-bucket valve adjustment for optimal timing. The drivetrain utilizes the iconic Getrag 265 dog-leg five-speed manual gearbox, feeding power to a 4.10 limited-slip rear differential. The suspension has been meticulously maintained with Bilstein dampers and refreshed bushings, ensuring the chassis retains its legendary turn-in response and torsional rigidity. Zero corrosion on the undercarriage and factory-spec BBS basketweave wheels. A mechanically transparent, turn-key investment for the serious purist.",
